metadata.name: Through the Looking-Glass 001
metadata.description:
Through the Looking-Glass is my genesis collection, taken on a variety of different streets from around the world, but with a deliberate focus on abstraction, bold colours, and mystery.

001 was captured in Whitstable, Kent, one early morning.

This is the first of 30 1/1 images, with the last image being minted on my 30th birthday.
